data.description: Come see this BETTER THAN NEW home in desirable Hunters Crossing! You'll love the ease of flow this home provides, from the south-facing front porch to the beautiful back deck overlooking your already landscaped, fully-fenced backyard. Spend time with friends and family in the open kitchen and dining area, then retreat to your primary suite w/ full bath and walk-in closet. Two additional nice-sized bedrooms offer space for everyone. And speaking of space, just think of what you can create in the full unfinished basement w/ rough-in plumbing! With brand new carpet throughout and central A/C installed, this home has been Pre-Inspected and is move-in ready. All you'll have to do is unpack!
